Netizen contribution
According to Jiupai News, a section chief of the Animal Husbandry Administration Bureau of Yushu City, Jilin Province, is suspected of raping and molesting elementary school girls.
Colleagues said that his wife is an elementary school teacher and heard that several rural students in the class were boarding at his home.
Currently, the section chief has been detained by the public security organs.

Recently, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security website released the minimum wage standards in various regions across the country (as of April 1, 2023). The monthly minimum wage standards in 15 regions are 2,000 yuan or more. Among them, Shanghai still ranks first with 2,590 yuan.
